Description
-----------

Controls which image to blend a [visportals](Visportal) to when it's closing.

Usage
-----

In the global section of your material shader type...

`portalImageÂ [map]`

Parameters
----------

-   [map] - the relative path and file name to the specified portal image.

Notes
-----

Usually the image used is "\_black". See also the [portaldistancefar](Portaldistancefar\_(Material\_global\_keyword)) and [portaldistancenear](Portaldistancenear\_(Material\_global\_keyword)) keywords.


